    <item>
      <title>中国要求贸易商限制部分海外玉米抵达</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/china-asks-traders-to-curb-some-arrivals-of-overseas-corn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海关已要求一些贸易商限制向保税区运送外国玉米，此举旨在缓解国内供应过剩，并在种植季节之前为农民提供价格支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/china-asks-traders-to-curb-some-arrivals-of-overseas-corn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
