      <title>随着选举风险过去，土耳其市场出现救济性反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/turkish-markets-swept-up-in-relief-rally-as-election-risk-passes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安表示支持现状经济政策后，里拉升值，政府债券上涨，确保土耳其债务违约的成本下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/turkish-markets-swept-up-in-relief-rally-as-election-risk-passes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果在经历十年来最糟糕的季度后调整支持水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/apple-flirts-with-support-levels-after-worst-quarter-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着苹果公司股价经历了十多年来相对于标准普尔 500 指数而言最糟糕的季度，交易员正在寻找最糟糕时期可能已经过去的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/apple-flirts-with-support-levels-after-worst-quarter-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>复苏迹象未能提振人民币情绪，人民币面临越来越大的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/yuan-faces-mounting-pressure-as-green-shoots-fail-to-lift-mood</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人民币距离在岸交易区间的弱端仅一步之遥，这是近期一系列乐观经济数据不足以提振人民币的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/yuan-faces-mounting-pressure-as-green-shoots-fail-to-lift-mood</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 09:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将扩大预算缺口 42 亿美元以刺激经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁已批准一项计划，将明年的预算赤字目标扩大约42亿美元，以帮助刺激东南亚第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
